{"snp5.18:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.18 ","snp5.18:0.2":"Parayanatthutigatha ","snp5.18:1.1":"Idamavoca bhagava magadhesu viharanto pasanake cetiye, ","snp5.18:1.2":"paricarakasolasanam brahmananam ajjhittho puttho puttho panham byakasi. ","snp5.18:1.3":"Ekamekassa cepi panhassa atthamannaya dhammamannaya dhammanudhammam patipajjeyya, gaccheyyeva jaramaranassa param. ","snp5.18:1.4":"Parangamaniya ime dhammati, tasma imassa dhammapariyayassa parayananteva adhivacanam. ","snp5.18:2.1":"Ajito tissametteyyo, ","snp5.18:2.2":"punnako atha mettagu; ","snp5.18:2.3":"Dhotako upasivo ca, ","snp5.18:2.4":"nando ca atha hemako. ","snp5.18:3.1":"Todeyya-kappa dubhayo, ","snp5.18:3.2":"jatukanni ca pandito; ","snp5.18:3.3":"Bhadravudho udayo ca, ","snp5.18:3.4":"posalo capi brahmano; ","snp5.18:3.5":"Mogharaja ca medhavi, ","snp5.18:3.6":"pingiyo ca mahaisi. ","snp5.18:4.1":"Ete buddham upagacchum, ","snp5.18:4.2":"sampannacaranam isim; ","snp5.18:4.3":"Pucchanta nipune panhe, ","snp5.18:4.4":"buddhasettham upagamum. ","snp5.18:5.1":"Tesam buddho pabyakasi, ","snp5.18:5.2":"panhe puttho yathatatham; ","snp5.18:5.3":"Panhanam veyyakaranena, ","snp5.18:5.4":"tosesi brahmane muni. ","snp5.18:6.1":"Te tosita cakkhumata, ","snp5.18:6.2":"buddhenadiccabandhuna; ","snp5.18:6.3":"Brahmacariyamacarimsu, ","snp5.18:6.4":"varapannassa santike. ","snp5.18:7.1":"Ekamekassa panhassa, ","snp5.18:7.2":"yatha buddhena desitam; ","snp5.18:7.3":"Tatha yo patipajjeyya, ","snp5.18:7.4":"gacche param aparato. ","snp5.18:8.1":"Apara param gaccheyya, ","snp5.18:8.2":"bhavento maggamuttamam; ","snp5.18:8.3":"Maggo so param gamanaya, ","snp5.18:8.4":"tasma parayanam iti. "}